ai.grakn.graql.internal.reasoner.query

Class ReasonerAtomicQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.graql.internal.reasoner.query.ReasonerQueryImpl
      • ai.grakn.graql.internal.reasoner.query.ReasonerAtomicQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReasonerQuery

    public class ReasonerAtomicQuery
extends ReasonerQueryImpl

    Base reasoner atomic query. An atomic query is a query constrained to having at most one rule-resolvable atom together with its accompanying constraints (predicates and types)

    Author:
    Kasper Piskorski
